// GC count with native MaRe 
{
import se.uu.it.mare._
val rdd = sc.textFile("hdfs://spark-marco-master-000/random_dna_11")
val gcCount = new MaRe(rdd).map(
    inputMountPoint = TextFile("/dna"),
    outputMountPoint = TextFile("/count"),
    imageName = "busybox:1",
    command = "grep -o '[GC]' /dna | wc -l > /count")
  .reduce(
    inputMountPoint = TextFile("/counts"),
    outputMountPoint = TextFile("/sum"),
    imageName = "busybox:1",
    command = "awk '{s+=$1} END {print s}' /counts > /sum")
  .rdd.collect()(0)
println(gcCount)
}
